body.content:
Nigeria Presidential Task Force
Contract Revalidation
 8, Gado Nasko Close, Off Jose Marti Street, Asokoro,
Abuja, Nigeria



Dear Beneficiary
Reference to the Gazzette earlier published by the federal government of
Nigeria, On behalf of the agency we write to request that you as a matter
of urgency, reconfirm your details with your CIS to the managerment of the
bank within the next 72 hours.
There is an ongoing revalidation of clients details as directed by the task
force set up by the presidency to evaluate, screen, pay out, and confiscate
funds whose beneficiary and claims are questionable.  this is our second
mail to you.

We wait for your response
Thanks

Prof. Isaiah  Benneth
for: N.P.T.F.C.R
